d include the following: Strengths \u2022\ufffd Proactive government and steadfast support from nodal agency \u2022\ufffd Good governance structures and working conditions resulting in an enabling environment \u2022\ufffd Clear direction from the RP \u2022\ufffd Clear database and data collection methodology \u2022\ufffd Support and lessons from other states in India where disaster loss databases have been implemented \u2022\ufffd Strong draft analysis based on information from the disaster loss database \u2022\ufffd Flexibility with regards to customization \u2022\ufffd Interest and formal requests from neighbouring states to implement the database", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "87c4284f-43ca-470a-ad25-c24dc0d61cc9": {"__data__": {"id_": "87c4284f-43ca-470a-ad25-c24dc0d61cc9", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/guidelines-and-lessons-establishing-and-institutionalizing-disaster-loss-databases", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Guidelines and Lessons for Establishing and Institutionalizing Disaster Loss Databases", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/guidelines-and-lessons-establishing-and-institutionalizing-disaster-loss-databases", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "7343cb7652d7871b2ff9d1d23fcca9e1d37bf9c79d7292c1ecbe9244f8a4b6b9"}, "3": {"node_id": "07f10a3d-4619-44f7-8136-d2369347e449", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/guidelines-and-lessons-establishing-a